    "slug": "leading-pharma-brand-programmatic-dooh-philippines",
    "title": "How a Leading Pharmaceutical Brand Engaged Health-Conscious Audiences Through Programmatic DOOH in the Philippines",
    "brand": "",
    "country": "Philippines",
    "industry": "Technology",
